<br />
Spells don't affect mobs in water unless you're in the water yourself. I took a while to figure this out when my Necro was fear-kiting the spectres in a group... I was snaring, cleric was fearing, and my pet and the melees ran after the spectre to kill it, but I kept snaring them before they got onto the beach and the snare spell would hit but do nothing.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
