				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Best tactic for this is make sure you have sow + levi and mem Cinder Bolt. Go to the island and pull one with cinder bolt. Pull it off to the main land then do as follows :
<br />

<br />
1) Get a good distance ahead of the spectres (kite them along P2, nice stretch of land there thats on water)
<br />
2) Get really far ahead
<br />
3) Start casting Cinder Bolt
<br />
4) Once Cinder Bolt stops move far away and do again
<br />

<br />
Cinder Bolt is a bolt nuke so it might hit a different spectre if it gets in way, if this happens don't worry it's all going to the same cause. Keep doing this, if you have KEI you can do it uber easy. Just keep moving and nuking. Thats what I did for quite a few levels <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> Safe Exp<br />_________________<br />"Better to remain silent and be thought a fool, than to speak and remove all doubt." 
<br />
                                         - Abraham Lincoln
<br />
"If you try to fail and succeed, which have you done?"                               - George Carlin</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
